flowchart TD

A[Game Start] --> B[Load Level Grid]
B --> C[Spawn Pac-Man]
C --> D[Spawn Ghosts]
D --> E[Enter GameState: Playing]

E --> F{Pac-Man Dead?}
F -- Yes --> G[Decrease Lives]
G --> H{Lives > 0?}
H -- Yes --> C[Respawn Pac-Man + Ghosts]
H -- No --> Z[Game Over]

F -- No --> I{All Pellets Eaten?}
I -- Yes --> J[Load Next Level]
J --> B

I -- No --> K[Gameplay Loop]

K --> L[Pac-Man Moves]
L --> M[Pac-Man Collides with Pellet?]
M -- Yes --> N[Emit: PelletEaten Event]

K --> O[Pac-Man Collides with Power Pellet?]
O -- Yes --> P[Emit: PowerPellet Eaten]
P --> Q[Ghosts Switch to Frightened Mode]

K --> R[Ghost AI Update]
R --> S[Ghost Collides with Pac-Man?]

S -- Yes AND Ghost is Frightened --> T[Emit GhostEaten Event]
S -- Yes AND Ghost is Normal --> F

S -- No --> E
